<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>ReqApp</title>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    "application", media: "all", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag "application", "data-turbolinks-track" => true %>
  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
</head>
<body class="<%= controller.controller_name %>">
  <div id="header">
    <%= link_to 'Welcome to Request Trap tool.','/', class: 'home-page-link'%>
    <ul>
      <li id="about-btn">About</li>
      <li>Log in</li>
      <li>Sign in</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="about">
    <p>   A tool for capture and display HTTP requests.
    <p>This simple tool is useful during the development of apps that
      integrate with external services, such as http clients, webhooks, etc.
    <p>The Requests Trap app ('Req App') provides these services with
      an endpoint to which they can send requests and notifications.
  </div>
  <div id="main">
    <%= yield %>
  </div>
  <div id="footer">
  </div>
</body>
</html>
